## Extended Worked Examples (Pattern Library)

Use these as **templates** — swap nouns for your domain.

### 1 — Digital service with external dependency
Async job + status polling; idempotency; vendor timeout + retry + DLQ; metrics on job outcomes; user sees progress not spinner forever.

### 2 — Batch sync (data or physical counts)
Watermark/cursor; single-flight lock; row/item quarantine; alert on error rate threshold; reconcile totals.

### 3 — Multi-tenant isolation (SaaS, housing, healthcare networks)
Tenant ID on every access path; cache keys scoped; penetration test scenario "tenant A reads tenant B"; default-deny.

### 4 — Real-time collaboration (docs, design, control room)
Auth on join; presence; conflict resolution strategy explicit; reconnect with jitter after deploy.

### 5 — Marketplace liquidity
Chicken-and-egg: subsidize supply or demand? Trust: reviews, escrow, dispute resolution; anti-leakage.

### 6 — Manufacturing line changeover
SMED principles; FAI; control plan update; operator training sign-off; revert to old tooling within X hours if yield drops.

### 7 — Clinical pathway tweak
Evidence citation; clinician override with reason; monitor adverse proxy; IRB/ethics if research.

### 8 — School scheduling / rostering
Hard constraints (room capacity) vs soft (teacher preference); explainability for parents; appeal path.

### 9 — Nonprofit program expansion
Theory of change mapped; measure outcomes not outputs; donor reporting aligned; don't collapse under admin load.

### 10 — Crisis comms protocol
Single source of truth; pre-approved templates; role roster; drill before the hurricane season / breach / recall.

### 11 — IoT fleet firmware OTA
Staged rollout; dual bank; automatic rollback on health metric; signing keys protected; bricking postmortem unacceptable.

### 12 — Pricing change
Segment analysis; grandfathering; communication timing; competitor response scenario; margin floor guardrail.

### 13 — Hiring loop redesign
Structured interviews; rubrics; debiasing checks; time-to-hire vs quality tradeoff explicit; candidate experience.

### 14 — Content moderation at scale
Severity tiers; SLA per tier; reviewer wellness; audit sample; adversarial evolution expected.

### 15 — M&A integration (systems + people)
Day-1 invariants (payroll, safety); integration factory; culture clash risks; retain critical tacit knowledge.

### 16 — Personal knowledge system / docs
Discoverability; ownership; stale content decay; don't duplicate canonical sources.

### 17 — Cursor rule / agent instruction (meta)
Scope control (alwaysApply vs globs); non-contradiction with other rules; test on sample tasks; length vs compliance tradeoff.

