## Practical Master Checklist (Any Feature, Any Domain)

Run proportionate to scope. For non-trivial work, every section gets at least one line.

### Problem
- [ ] What exact problem exists? Why does it exist?
- [ ] Root cause or symptom?
- [ ] What human need does this compress (not which tech)?

### Users & stakeholders
- [ ] Who benefits? Who loses? Who bears cost without benefit?
- [ ] What behavior changes? How might they game it?

### System
- [ ] System type(s): state / information / decision / constraint / optimization / economic / reliability / human?
- [ ] Inputs, outputs, state transitions, flows (info, money, trust, control, failure propagation)?
- [ ] Invariants stated as testable claims?

### Constraints
- [ ] Technical, human, business, organizational limits identified?
- [ ] Hidden constraints others ignored — opportunity or trap?

### Tradeoffs & objective function
- [ ] What are we maximizing? What worsens when we win?
- [ ] Priority stack explicit (no hidden ranking)?
- [ ] ≥2 designs compared; loser explained?

### Failure (seven paths)
- [ ] Happy · expected bad · adversarial · scale · time · dependency · human psychology?
- [ ] Failure types: technical, logical, human, economic, scaling, security, trust, incentive, organizational?

### Scale & irreversibility
- [ ] What breaks at 10× / 100× / 1000×?
- [ ] **What is the irreversible consequence if this succeeds massively?**
- [ ] What if it works **too well**?

### Security & trust
- [ ] Exploit surfaces? Trust failures? Data exposure?

### Economics & leverage
- [ ] Build + maintain + infra + support + cognitive + migration cost?
- [ ] Revenue / retention / moat / trust impact?
- [ ] Value Created ÷ Complexity Added favorable?

### Observability
- [ ] How will we know it works or fails?
- [ ] Baseline for comparison? Who watches which signal?

### Evolution
- [ ] How does this adapt as scale, models, regulation, behavior change?
- [ ] Cost of future change? Rollback path?

### AI-specific (when applicable)
- [ ] Hidden assumptions enumerated?
- [ ] Dangerous hallucinations identified?
- [ ] Validation layers before irreversible actions?
- [ ] Agent used for design critique before code?

